        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好奇怪啊……\\n应该就在这附近才是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅，你也该告诉我们了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "为什么又回到圣树来？\\n这里有对抗“起始之人”的方法吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也许有，也许没有。\\n所以才要来找啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "不要说得这么模棱两可。\\n也许我们在做这些事情的时候\\n“起始之人”就已经复活了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好好好，我知道啦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "如果我的推理没错，\\n“起始之人”至少已经\\n复活过一次。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么意思？\\n你说这话有什么证据吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "证据……就是我和塞西娅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过，我并不敢断定如此。\\n所以才会来这里确认。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "圣树自古以来就存在。\\n“起始之人”和“起始之龙”的年代起\\n就已经有圣树了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "而从那时至今的所有记忆\\n都沉睡在这棵圣树之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "若如我所料，“起始之人”\\n过去曾复活过一次的话，\\n那么应该会留有当时的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "既然如此，\\n我们直接问圣树的意志不就好了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "若是这方法可行的话就不用这么辛苦了。\\n遗憾的是，圣树记忆的量\\n远非一个意志可以承受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "因此圣树才会将记忆和意志分离，\\n保存在树干或根部。\\n我们现在要找的就是那个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "毕竟是相当古老的记忆，\\n我猜应该在根部。能下到\\n那里去的树洞应该就在这附近……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "噢！找到了找到了。\\n走，我们继续前进吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这里……留有圣树的记忆？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "与其说是圣树的记忆，\\n不如说是世界的记忆。\\n因为圣树和全世界的魔力源点相连。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们要从中寻找“起始之人”\\n出现在这个世界时的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你说要寻找……\\n可这到底要怎么找才好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你无路可逃了！\\n魔神……莫尔托梅塞亚！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我要在此地，再次将你封印！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶！？刚、刚才那是！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那就是圣树的记忆。\\n看起来应该是300年前左右的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "似乎是阿尔贝琉斯和\\n莫尔托梅塞亚战斗时的记忆啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们要找的是更加古老的记忆。\\n一定还在更深处，\\n我们加快脚步前进吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "伊莉雅！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "哦、哦……是圣树的记忆啊……\\n吓了我一跳……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "梅奈……\\n这应该是1000年前的记忆吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "怎么会这样……\\n伊莉雅！开门……求你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "伊莉雅啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "真伤脑筋……\\n没想到会以这种形式\\n被迫目睹自己的不孝之举。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但我却不能沉浸在悲伤之中\\n就此止步不前……\\n我还真是不孝啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没事的，\\n梅奈一定会理解你的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯……\\n那我走了，梅奈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我们已经下到相当深的地方了，\\n这里保留的会是\\n多久以前的记忆呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "刚才已经走过古代麒麟文明的记忆了，\\n这里应该是几万年前没错……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "归根结底，\\n“起始之人”曾复活过一次这个假设\\n本就没有确切的证据。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我们也许根本是白忙一场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "可我觉得应该确有其事……\\n真奇怪……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“起始之人”——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "啊！？你们听！\\n刚才有声音说“起始之人”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01",
                "100048_01",
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这是……黑暗魔力……\\n唔……明明只是记忆，\\n竟会有如此让人痛苦的压力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "是“起始之人”……\\n“起始之人”就在\\n这黑暗魔力的另一侧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯……这一定就是\\n“起始之人”曾经复活时的记忆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "为了这个世界……必须守护……\\n可能性……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "原来是圣域龙……\\n在与“起始之人”战斗吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "快看！还有别的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120250_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我们必须要阻止……\\n世界的末路……全新的世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120252_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "虽不情愿……哪怕散为魔力……\\n别无选择……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120251_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "开什么玩笑……我不吭声……\\n可别太小看我了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120253_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "就算耍了手段……\\n身为龙也觉得不舒服……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120254_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "扭曲的世界……绝望……\\n为害世间之……我的骄傲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120254_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "刚、刚才那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "看来是记忆太过古老。\\n很多部分都断断续续，\\n听得人云里雾里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但这应该是圣域龙与其他众龙\\n一同击退“起始之人”时的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "与其说是击退，更像是阻止其复活，\\n或是说再次封印他的情形。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "即便如此，对现在的我们来说\\n也是极其珍贵的信息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "因为这说明只要汇聚众龙的力量\\n就能对抗“起始之人”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
